snippet.title: 공기남 - My Favorite (Feat. Akita) [Short Lyric Video]
snippet.description:
공기남 - My Favorite (Feat. Akita) [Short Lyric Video]

싱어송라이터 ‘공기남’이 전하는 감성 에세이 앨범.
‘Freshman Series’ 그 일곱 번째 이야기. [My Favorite]

“You are all of my favorite things.”

Track list.
01. My Favorite (Feat. Akita) (작사 : 공기남 / 작곡 : 공기남 / 편곡 : 공기남, 양혁, KOO)
02. My Favorite (Inst.) (작곡 : 공기남 / 편곡 : 공기남, 양혁, KOO )

[Credits]
Executive producer 공기남
Lyrics by 공기남
Composed by 공기남
Arranged by 공기남, 양혁, KOO
Vocal by 공기남, Akita
Chorus by 공기남, 고남준
Piano by 공기남
Guitar by YOUNG
Bass by 공기남, KOO
Drum by 공기남, 양혁, KOO
Midi Programing by 공기남, 양혁, KOO
Recorded by fovitz @AirMusic Studio
Mixed by fovitz @AirMusic Studio
Mastered by 권남우 @821 Sound
Album artwork by Saydung @saydung.89
Management Airmusic
Team leader 박지호 @melanoalbinc
